NUMBER 1681
NAME Marren's Pride, Control Room
INDOOR_FLOOR
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
The control room is a marvelous blend of technology and Maratasen tradition.
It is circular, with a domed ceiling made of a material that uniformly
illuminates the room with a pleasant golden glow. The floor is made of a soft
golden brown material that yields slightly underfoot as though it were natural
earth. The walls seem to flow out of the floor and ceiling, gradually changing
color and texture. At the center of the room is a semicircular console covered
with a multitude of readouts and control studs interspersed with exotic
carvings. Several bowl-shaped chairs are located near a raised platform.
*DESCRIPTION_END

; Ceiling
ITEM 0 482
; Console
ITEM 1 718
; Chair
ITEM 2 86
; Chair
ITEM 3 86
; Platform
ITEM 4 365
; Floor
ITEM 5 1677
IFVERB TOUCH 5
  ECHO PLAYER It feels like soft, spongy earth, but is made up of a strong, artificial substance.
ENDIF

IFVERB LISTEN -1
  ECHO PLAYER You hear the faint humm of machinery.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LOOK 2
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The chair is bowl-shaped and looks quite comfortable.
ENDIF

IFVERB SMELL -1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 126
    ECHO PLAYER Ah, the familiar smells of your ship were carefully selected and blended to create a pleasing and tranquil environment.
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER  You catch odd smells that seem to change over time. After a moment, you notice that the lights in the control panel seem to be in synch with the changes.
    IFVAR RAC = 4

    ELSE
      IFVAR RAC = 7
        ECHO PLAYER Your mechanical senses pick each scent from the air and analyze them. Interestingly, they seem to be blended to produce a calming effect on the Maratasen mind.
      ELSE
        ECHO PLAYER The air is filled with a pleasant mixture of different scents.
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LOOK 1
  ECHO PLAYER The main console seems to be carved from a single block of stone which is
  ECHO PLAYER covered with carvings of a pride of Maratasens chasing herds of antlered
  ECHO PLAYER beasts. The Maratasen are armed with only their teeth and claws, but that
  ECHO PLAYER seems to be more than enough, as they pull the giant animals to the ground.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  ECHO PLAYER Through the ceiling, you see very convincing images of thunderclouds high
  ECHO PLAYER above you. They move slowly across the sky, occasionally being illuminated
  ECHO PLAYER by a fork of lightning.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LOOK 4
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The platform is large enough for several people to stand on. Its brightly-
  ECHO PLAYER glowing surface is engraved with various sun-symbols.
ENDIF

IFSAY TA'CHA
  ECHO ALL The walls emit a series of soft high-pitched tones.
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The displays over the forward wall gain intensity.
ENDIF

IFSAY TA'NOK
  ECHO ALL The walls emit a series of soft high-pitched tones.
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The displays along the forward wall dim, causing the room to grow darker.
ENDIF

IFSAY KAR'CA
  ECHO ALL The walls emit a series of soft high-pitched tones.
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL A deep female voice speaks rapidly from all about the room. The voice seems to punctuate as various screens light up, displaying information that you cannot decypher.
ENDIF

IFSAY NOK'CHA!
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 126
    ECHO ALL An iris forms over the wall, twisting to reveal an opening into the other room.
    NEWITEM 7 72 VAL2=1682
  ELSE
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GO 7
  ECHO OTHGROUP The opening shuts behind %N.
  REMOVEITEM 7
  MOVEGROUP 1682
  ECHO GROUP The opening twists shut behind you.
  AFFECT 1682
  ECHO OTHGROUP %N arrives through an opening, which twists shut behind %i.
  AFFECT 1681
ENDIF

IFSAY PATE!
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 126
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    AFFECT 206
    ECHO ALL Suddenly, you are bathed in a tremendous white glow!
    ECHO ALL %N appears!
    AFFECT 1681
    ECHO ALL The platform hums and extends around the circumference of the room. A bright light envelops you, and suddenly you are elsewhere...
    MOVEALL 206
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFSAY PU'CHA
  ECHO ALL The walls emit a series of soft high-pitched tones.
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The walls of the room dim for a moment, then begin to shine brightly.
ENDIF

IFSAY PU'TAK
  ECHO ALL The walls emit a series of soft high-pitched tones.
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The walls of the room glow brightly for a moment, then dim to a comfortable level.
ENDIF

IFSAY PU'NOK
  ECHO ALL The walls emit a series of soft high-pitched tones.
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The walls of the room glow dimly for a moment, then go out.
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 1682
NAME Marren's Pride, Stateroom
INDOOR_FLOOR
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
This room, while similar to the control room in shape and construction, has a
smaller, cozier feeling to it. The lighting is more subdued, and the colors
used have been muted. As in the control room, the image projected from the
ceiling is that of the sky. Here, however, the image is broken up and tinted
into leaf patterns to simulate a grove of trees. The floor is covered in soft,
luxuriant animal hides, a huge pile of pillows, and cushions. The walls are
paneled in richly stained wood and are covered with shelves of animal
trophies, maratasen weapons and large tapestries. An android shaped vaguely
into the form of a maratasen sits below several shelves.
*DESCRIPTION_END

; Shelf
ITEM 0 848
EXTEND 0 to the left of the maratasen android
; Shelf
ITEM 1 848
EXTEND 1 to the right of the maratasen android
; Shelf
ITEM 2 848
EXTEND 2 above the maratasen android

IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER On the shelf is a huge double edged blade with an intricately inlaid scene of
  ECHO PLAYER a female Maratasen kneeling before a great shining light. The blade is fully
  ECHO PLAYER 5 feet long and looks heavy.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LOOK 1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER This is a rack of Claw Gloves. It would seem that the gloves are intended to
  ECHO PLAYER be worn in combat to protect the fingers and hands as much as possible but
  ECHO PLAYER still allowing the claws to be used.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LOOK 2
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER This seems to be a wild jumble of animal parts taken form many exotic animals
  ECHO PLAYER and carefully preserved and mounted. The central piece of the display is the
  ECHO PLAYER head rack of the giant beasts carved in the control consoles.
ENDIF

IFVERB SNIFF -1
  ECHO PLAYER A pleasant mix various grasses and other flora fills the air.
ENDIF

IFVERB LISTEN -1
  ECHO PLAYER You hear the faint rustle of wind moving through tall grasses. You can also make out the sounds of what might be animals indigenous to the maratasen world.
ENDIF

IFSAY TAAL
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
