IFVAR DUMMY1 = 1
  ECHO ALL The central panel lights up and begins to scroll through pages of a strange flowing golden script.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 2
  ECHO ALL Brilliant golden symbols form over the surface of the display to your right.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 3
  ECHO ALL The ship bobs up and down slightly.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 4
  ECHO ALL The ground jerks beneath your feet. A low-pitched klaxon sounds, but ceases after a moment.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 5
  ECHO ALL The ship tilts slightly, then rights itself.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 6
  ECHO ALL One of the central panels emits a series of soft, high-pitched tones.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 7
  ECHO ALL One of the displays comes to life with the image of a large, blue planet with scarred blotches of tan. From ths vantage point, the world looks peaceful.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 8
  ECHO ALL A central console displays the image of the dark side of Andor. Slowly, the sun comes into view, washing the planet with a golden light.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 9
  ECHO ALL A screen flickers on, displaying the image of a very large ship moving towards you at a rapid pace. Rainbows of light streak from the ship's engines as the view rotates around it.
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 10
  ECHO ALL One of the screens showing Andor from orbit zooms in on Fayd, giving a detailed image of the city's layout.
ENDIF
;
