variable IDCokay
variable IDCto
variable IDCnoport
variable IDCalert
;
number 3530
name Shuttle, Transporter Room
channel 1315
astral
*description_start
The rectangular room is covered with charcoal gray wall panels and has a
ceiling bearing segmented lighting units. Against one wall is a control panel
which bears the remnants of a convoluted series of knobs and levers. Towards
the center of the room is a circular platform.
*description_end
item 1 365 adj1=976 adj2=693
item 2 282 adj1=1463
item 3 802
item 4 1341 val2=3532
ifpreverb look 1
  clearverb
  echo player The raised platform is large enough for several people to stand on.
endif
ifpreverb look 2
  clearverb
  echo player The control panel seems to have originally been covered with various controls, but they have been done away with and replaced by a small slot.
endif

ifpreverb look 3
  clearverb
  echo player It's a slot, plain and simple. Its function is unclear.
endif

iftouch 4
  ifvar IDCokay = 0
    clearverb
    echo player You are interposed by an invisible force!
    echo others %N is thrown back as %h steps towards a doorway!
    plrevent 2
    contplrevent
    echo all A voice intones, "Security systems are still active per order of User Cyrano DeBergerac."
  endif
endif

ifpreverb go 1
     ifvar flag1 = 449
  clearverb
  echo player You're already standing there.
     else
  clearverb
  echo player You step onto the platform.
  echo others %P steps onto the platform.
  equal flag1 449
     endif
endif
ifsay COMPUTER,_DESTINATION_1.
  ifvar plrmark1 < 1
    echo all A voice intones, "Unable to obtain a lock on that destination."
  else
    equal IDCto plrmark1
    echo all A voice intones, "Confirmed."
  endif
endif
ifsay COMPUTER,_DESTINATION_2.
  ifvar plrmark2 < 2
    echo all A voice intones, "Unable to obtain a lock on that destination."
